\nthermal electrons within the optical shadow of Mars are up to 20% more likely\nto be observed when the strongest crustal magnetic fields point sunward than\nwhen they point tailward.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 18 Mar 2021 17:12:44 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-03-19"}
